{"tid":1507593,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【和理非】反對黨鐵助紂為虐 - 全民Gear搭地鐵活動開始!!!","createTime":"2019-08-26T08:19:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T07:04:12.000Z","uid":299212,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a0f6541b3f80ffce63f270f35fcbcafecd7f5319","tid":1507593,"uid":299212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T08:19:05.000Z","msg":"黨鐵過去一星期封鐵協助政權打壓示威者，又於多個安裝全新監控鏡頭，營造白色恐怖。<br />\n既然周圍都咁危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />危險到要關閉車站，又有催淚彈殘留物，作為一個普通市民，帶番啲裝備保護自己都好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由今日起 大家搭黨鐵既時候應該配備<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">頭盔</span></strong>, <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">眼罩</span></strong>與及<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">黑口罩</span></strong>，甚至係豬嘴，保護自己。<br />\n<br />\n以下幾點提議比番大家<br />\n1. 番學番工放工時間做，越多人做效果越好，人多亦唔易比人check身份證<br />\n2. 番工裝扮未必帶到頭盔，但唔戴都帶住，作為一個象徵，又或者只帶口罩眼罩<br />\n3. 真勇武就小心,比人check身份證留record就麻煩<br />\n4. 只帶防具, 只係要保護自己<br />\n5. 9月開學日一定要帶<br />\n<br />\n當人人都有頭盔口罩係身既時候，就可以淡化帶gear本身既奇怪，保護大家，亦比一份支持勇武。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>遊行唔係淨係星期六日，全民GEAR!</strong></span></span><br />\n之前法律界遊行圖片參考<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cuM6sHt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcuM6sHt.jpg&h=3ce4e612&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7891d42a33304c2d971fbac0f9c98fb6150e648b","tid":1507593,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T08:19:27.000Z","msg":"［解放殖民，香港革命］昨晚，打響了香港革命的第一槍<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1507581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1507581</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d22b7cc534f4ce00b689707ca7f536252609ecec","tid":1507593,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T08:19:38.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個post宣傳一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GJMrJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3